{"body": "@jridgewell if you are willing to work on this (@shuber seems to be busy right now), you should open a new PR.\r\n\r\nThe best fix for this is just to add a `to_prepare` callback instead of mucking with `NullStore`:\r\n\r\n```ruby\r\n# in actionpack/lib/action_view/railtie.rb\r\nif in_development? && caching_is_enabled?\r\n  ActionDispatch::Reloader.to_prepare { ActionView::Digestor.cache.clear }\r\nend\r\n```\r\n\r\nDon't forget to document it, close all the relevant issues and a test case would also be nice :) :heart:.\r\n\r\n", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/21996590", "created_at": "2013-08-02T09:56:22Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/10791#issuecomment-21996590", "updated_at": "2013-08-02T09:56:22Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 10791, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/thedarkone/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/thedarkone/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/thedarkone/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/thedarkone", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/thedarkone/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/thedarkone", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/thedarkone/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://1.gravatar.com/avatar/c203190318ed9534390c93d1744a6cf1?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F68e4593563e1b425a7717504bca103d6.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/thedarkone/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/thedarkone/received_events", "gravatar_id": "c203190318ed9534390c93d1744a6cf1", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/thedarkone/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "thedarkone", "type": "User", "id": 15688, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/thedarkone/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "5237dbb8bd3543c1510088c8"}, "id": 21996590, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/10791"}
